WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.869
Hey, good morning family! I am so excited

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:04.670
to come on today and give you the word

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:06.869
that the Lord has for you. I was

00:00:06.879 --> 00:00:08.350
praying and just asking, 'Lord, what

00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:10.950
do you have for your people

00:00:10.950 --> 00:00:10.960
today?'and

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:12.709
He said, 'I want you to tell them this:

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:14.470
for the eyes of the Lord are running to

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:16.590
and fro throughout the whole earth

00:00:16.600 --> 00:00:19.349
looking for a heart who's perfect toward

00:00:19.349 --> 00:00:19.359
Him.'My

00:00:19.359 --> 00:00:23.189
message today is: How big, how bad

00:00:23.199 --> 00:00:26.230
is your 'want to'? You know what? If you

00:00:26.240 --> 00:00:28.750
want to go do things for Jesus and you

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.669
want to walk in the authority,

00:00:31.679 --> 00:00:33.549
the power, and the victory of the

00:00:33.559 --> 00:00:36.630
Lord, you've got to have a strong 'want to'.

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:38.630
You've got to have a great desire to

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:42.270
serve Him and a great yielded 'want to'.

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:44.830
There was one time

00:00:44.830 --> 00:00:44.840
when

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.709
I was a little boy, I

00:00:47.719 --> 00:00:51.590
had warts all over my body. They

00:00:51.590 --> 00:00:51.600
were

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:54.110
covering me from the top of my

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:56.270
head, all over my chest, and all

00:00:56.280 --> 00:01:01.029
over my back.

00:01:01.039 --> 00:01:03.590
Every day I got made fun of at

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:05.310
school because of those warts; they

00:01:05.320 --> 00:01:08.230
called me 'Wart Boy'. Every night I

00:01:08.240 --> 00:01:10.749
went home and, while getting ready for

00:01:10.759 --> 00:01:13.030
bed, I told my dad, 'I want you to

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:15.510
anoint every single one of those warts

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.070
with oil, and I'm believing I'm going to

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:20.270
be healed.'I was just seven years

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:22.710
old. Every night I would go in, and

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.429
even sometimes when he would forget and

00:01:25.429 --> 00:01:25.439
go

00:01:25.439 --> 00:01:27.749
to bed,

00:01:27.749 --> 00:01:27.759
I

00:01:27.759 --> 00:01:29.510
would go in

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.550
there: 'Daddy, you forgot to anoint my

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:34.910
warts with oil because I believe that Jesus

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:38.270
Christ was a

00:01:38.270 --> 00:01:38.280
healer.'He

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.789
would say, 'Oh son, I'm tired.'I said, 'Dad,

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:42.749
but you've got to! I believe I'm going to be

00:01:42.759 --> 00:01:46.109
healed. You've got to anoint these warts

00:01:46.109 --> 00:01:46.119
with oil.'So

00:01:46.119 --> 00:01:49.069
he anointed them, and this went on for

00:01:49.079 --> 00:01:52.230
probably close to a year, but my 'want

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:52.240
to'was

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:54.870
bigger than the

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:57.310
pain of having those warts all over my

00:01:57.320 --> 00:02:00.550
body. My 'want to'being healed was great.

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:02.469
So you've got to have a 'want

00:02:02.469 --> 00:02:02.479
to'that's

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:04.389
stronger than what your

00:02:04.399 --> 00:02:06.950
circumstances are. It doesn't matter whatever

00:02:06.950 --> 00:02:06.960
is

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:08.990
going on in your life or how big

00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:11.510
those circumstances may be. You may look

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:13.869
at it and think it's impossible, but if you

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:16.150
have a 'want to'that's strong enough and

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.309
a desire in your heart,

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:20.190
God's going to come

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:22.509
through for you. You've got to keep that

00:02:22.519 --> 00:02:25.190
'want to'strong. That

00:02:25.190 --> 00:02:25.200
'want to'was

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:26.830
inside of me; it kept coming back and

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:29.869
saying, 'Daddy, anoint those

00:02:29.879 --> 00:02:31.790
warts with oil, and Jesus is going to

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:34.949
heal me.'Well, one morning I woke up and

00:02:34.959 --> 00:02:37.790
they were laying all beside me in my bed.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:39.910
All those

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:42.750
warts had fallen off of my body. Glory to

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:45.470
God! They all fell off my body and Jesus

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:47.110
healed me in the middle of the night.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:49.190
I woke up the next

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:51.869
day and was completely delivered from

00:02:51.879 --> 00:02:54.550
all those warts. I ran in while my dad

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:57.110
was still asleep in bed, grabbed a

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.430
hold of his arm and said, 'Dad, look!

00:02:59.440 --> 00:03:01.550
Every one of the warts are

00:03:01.550 --> 00:03:01.560
gone!'They

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:04.229
were in piles in my bed.

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:06.830
Jesus Christ healed me from the top of

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:09.710
my head to the soles of my feet. I'm

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:11.949
here to tell you, if you have a 'want

00:03:11.949 --> 00:03:11.959
to'in

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:14.589
your heart that is strong enough that

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:19.110
says, 'I will have what I say, I will have

00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:21.550
what I believe, and I'm going to confess

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:24.110
that Jesus Christ is the healer,'He's a

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:27.190
deliverer. He is not a God

00:03:27.190 --> 00:03:27.200
who

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:29.750
is a respecter of persons, and if

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:31.830
He'll do it for me, He'll do it for you.

00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:33.509
That's the kind of

00:03:33.519 --> 00:03:36.030
faith you've got to have—that bulldog

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:38.710
faith that says, 'I'm not giving up; I'm

00:03:38.720 --> 00:03:41.229
going to keep on with my

00:03:41.229 --> 00:03:41.239
want to.'Blind Bartimaeus

00:03:41.239 --> 00:03:44.270
was at the gate and he

00:03:44.280 --> 00:03:47.550
was yelling, 'Jesus, Son of David,

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:50.270
have mercy on me!'He kept yelling and

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:52.270
they kept saying, 'Shut up, beggar! Shut up,

00:03:52.270 --> 00:03:52.280
Bartimaeus!'He

00:03:52.280 --> 00:03:54.350
was yelling while they tried to

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.149
shut him up,

00:03:56.159 --> 00:03:58.429
but his 'want to'was stronger

00:03:58.439 --> 00:04:00.470
because

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:04.309
he knew that if he could just have an

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:07.990
encounter with Jesus, his eyes would

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:10.949
be made whole. He probably heard

00:04:10.959 --> 00:04:12.390
about all the people that had been

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:14.470
healed before

00:04:14.470 --> 00:04:14.480
him—the

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:16.550
lepers walking down the

00:04:16.550 --> 00:04:16.560
path—because

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:17.990
he was out there all the time

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.629
begging for money.

00:04:23.960 --> 00:04:26.510
He had

00:04:26.520 --> 00:04:28.990
a great desire and a yielded 'want

00:04:28.990 --> 00:04:29.000
to'that

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.469
said, 'I want to be healed by this

00:04:31.479 --> 00:04:34.430
Jesus. Son of David, have mercy on

00:04:34.430 --> 00:04:34.440
me!'He

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:37.070
kept

00:04:37.080 --> 00:04:39.310
crying out because he had

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:44.110
an

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:46.870
anticipation of knowing that Jesus is a

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.950
healer. So he got his miracle, as we

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:53.310
all know the Word says, and he got his

00:04:53.320 --> 00:04:56.150
eyes healed. It's the same thing with

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:58.310
the woman with the issue of blood.

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.790
She spent all that she had,

00:05:00.800 --> 00:05:03.950
but yet rather grew worse, the Bible says.

00:05:03.960 --> 00:05:06.710
But she knew if she could just

00:05:06.710 --> 00:05:06.720
press—she

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.870
probably heard about the miracles too.

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.950
She was weak because she had an issue

00:05:10.960 --> 00:05:12.710
of blood; she kept

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.469
bleeding, and the doctors couldn't

00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:16.909
figure out how to fix her. But she

00:05:16.919 --> 00:05:19.230
had a 'want to'.

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:21.070
She kept going

00:05:21.080 --> 00:05:23.070
back to the doctor, saying, 'I'm not giving up; I

00:05:23.080 --> 00:05:25.510
want to be

00:05:25.510 --> 00:05:25.520
well.'Then

00:05:25.520 --> 00:05:28.390
she heard about Jesus and

00:05:28.400 --> 00:05:30.710
His miracles, so she went out

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:32.590
there and grabbed a hold of the hem

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:35.110
of His garment. Probably out of

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:36.909
exhaustion, she crawled up there,

00:05:38.440 --> 00:05:40.510
and virtue went out

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:43.909
of Jesus. He touched her and

00:05:43.919 --> 00:05:46.230
said, 'Daughter, your faith has made you

00:05:46.230 --> 00:05:46.240
whole.'It

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.629
was a

00:05:48.629 --> 00:05:48.639
'want to'that

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:51.070
was so strong she

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:55.150
said, 'I want to have my miracle

00:05:55.150 --> 00:05:55.160
today.'That's

00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:56.830
the kind of faith you've got to

00:05:56.840 --> 00:05:59.150
have. You've got to know that Jesus

00:05:59.160 --> 00:06:01.550
Christ is the same yesterday, today, and

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:03.550
forever, and He's still doing

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:05.749
miracles today.

00:06:05.759 --> 00:06:07.909
If you want your kids to be born

00:06:07.919 --> 00:06:09.950
again and serving God,

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:12.749
you say, 'I'm going to have children that

00:06:12.759 --> 00:06:15.309
serve God. I'm going to have kids that

00:06:15.319 --> 00:06:17.550
are on fire for

00:06:17.550 --> 00:06:17.560
God.'Well,

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:19.230
you've got to have a 'want to'big enough

00:06:19.240 --> 00:06:21.510
to put them in church on Sundays

00:06:21.510 --> 00:06:21.520
and

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:23.749
Wednesdays, keep them

00:06:23.759 --> 00:06:25.230
around the youth group, and keep them

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:27.430
around praise and worship.

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:29.589
You've got to teach them the Word

00:06:29.599 --> 00:06:32.150
in the house. How big, how bad is your

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:34.670
'want to'? How bad do you want

00:06:34.680 --> 00:06:36.790
to be

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.469
filled with the Holy Ghost? There's some

00:06:38.479 --> 00:06:40.070
of you out there—I've seen the comment section—who

00:06:40.070 --> 00:06:40.080
say,

00:06:40.080 --> 00:06:42.430
'Well, I tried it for a couple

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:44.749
of minutes

00:06:44.759 --> 00:06:46.909
and it

00:06:46.919 --> 00:06:49.589
didn't work.'How bad is your 'want to'? There

00:06:49.599 --> 00:06:51.230
was a woman

00:06:51.230 --> 00:06:51.240
whose

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:53.469
husband was an alcoholic. He was

00:06:53.479 --> 00:06:55.189
out at the bars one night

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:58.070
drinking really bad, and she

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:00.670
knew the path he took home through the graveyard every night.

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:09.430
So she dug a six-foot hole

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:11.189
right in the path she knew he

00:07:11.199 --> 00:07:14.390
was going to walk. But another man came before

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.990
him and fell down in that hole. He

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:19.150
was tearing and clawing and

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:20.990
screaming, 'Help me! Help me!'but

00:07:20.990 --> 00:07:21.000
eventually

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:23.070
he gave up and

00:07:23.070 --> 00:07:23.080
sat

00:07:23.080 --> 00:07:24.790
in the corner

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.270
to

00:07:26.280 --> 00:07:29.430
wait for morning.

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:37.909
Lo and behold,

00:07:41.160 --> 00:07:43.830
that drunk husband came down

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:47.430
there

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:57.029
singing his song, and

00:07:57.039 --> 00:07:59.029
then, boom, he fell down in that

00:07:59.039 --> 00:08:01.550
hole. He sobered up real quick

00:08:01.560 --> 00:08:03.309
because he realized

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:05.390
he was stuck in

00:08:05.400 --> 00:08:07.309
a six-foot hole

00:08:07.309 --> 00:08:07.319
in

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:09.110
the

00:08:09.110 --> 00:08:09.120
graveyard.

00:08:09.120 --> 00:08:10.790
He was clawing

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:14.749
and yelling, 'Oh, help me! Help

00:08:14.749 --> 00:08:14.759
me!'and

00:08:14.759 --> 00:08:16.749
all of a sudden in the

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:19.990
darkness he heard, 'There's no one going

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:22.029
to help

00:08:22.029 --> 00:08:22.039
you.'Well,

00:08:22.039 --> 00:08:25.670
he got out of that hole! How bad

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:27.430
was his 'want to'? Whenever the devil's

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:28.909
trying to knock you

00:08:28.919 --> 00:08:30.869
down

00:08:30.869 --> 00:08:30.879
and

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:32.190
tell you that you're never going to amount

00:08:32.190 --> 00:08:32.200
to

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:33.829
anything,

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:45.030
you've got to tell

00:08:45.040 --> 00:08:47.750
him, 'No! Greater is He that is in me than

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:49.910
he that is in the world.'I'm not moved by

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:52.269
what I see or feel.

00:08:52.279 --> 00:08:54.829
Devil, you may try to knock me down, but

00:08:54.839 --> 00:08:56.949
I'm going to keep standing up.

00:08:56.959 --> 00:08:58.389
It's just like

00:08:58.389 --> 00:08:58.399
those

00:08:58.399 --> 00:08:59.870
old clown

00:08:59.880 --> 00:09:01.790
punching bags; you keep punching them, but they

00:09:01.790 --> 00:09:01.800
keep

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:03.389
rising back up. You

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:09.670
can't give in to the devil's torment.

00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:09.680
You've

00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:12.269
got to keep on with a 'want

00:09:12.269 --> 00:09:12.279
to'that's

00:09:12.279 --> 00:09:14.470
strong enough.

00:09:14.480 --> 00:09:16.750
'I want my house to be paid off! I

00:09:16.760 --> 00:09:18.949
want to be

00:09:18.949 --> 00:09:18.959
debt-free!'You've

00:09:18.959 --> 00:09:21.190
got

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:22.990
to be disciplined in your flesh,

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:24.910
save

00:09:24.910 --> 00:09:24.920
your

00:09:24.920 --> 00:09:26.590
money, and do what it takes. You've

00:09:26.590 --> 00:09:26.600
got

00:09:26.600 --> 00:09:29.630
to

00:09:29.630 --> 00:09:29.640
sow

00:09:29.640 --> 00:09:32.190
the seed at church, and

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.470
God said He'll bless everything you put

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:36.630
your hands to.

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:36.640
You've

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:38.990
got to know

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:41.230
that God is no respecter of persons.

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:43.350
What

00:09:43.350 --> 00:09:43.360
He'll

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:45.990
do for one, He'll do for you. I believe

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:48.190
with all my heart, but it takes a heart

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:51.430
of a 'want to'. For

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:54.470
the eyes of the Lord are running to and

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:56.990
fro throughout the whole earth looking

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:59.509
for a heart who's perfect toward Him.

00:09:59.509 --> 00:09:59.519
You've

00:09:59.519 --> 00:10:01.710
got to have that heart that's after God,

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:04.030
that says,

00:10:04.040 --> 00:10:07.630
'I want to be free from drugs, sin, sickness,

00:10:07.630 --> 00:10:07.640
and disease.'I

00:10:07.640 --> 00:10:10.790
want to be free from

00:10:13.200 --> 00:10:16.230
perversions and I

00:10:16.240 --> 00:10:19.030
want my marriage to be good. I want

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:22.150
my home to be a house that serves

00:10:22.160 --> 00:10:27.630
the Lord. How big, how bad is your 'want to'?

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:29.829
That's what I have for you today.

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:32.069
I'm telling you, I know beyond a shadow

00:10:32.079 --> 00:10:35.110
of a doubt, in all my times in my life, I've

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:37.350
always had that bulldog faith, and

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:38.870
that's why I'm still standing for my

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:40.670
little girl—that she's going to be

00:10:40.680 --> 00:10:43.110
healed. My want to is stronger than the

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:45.790
circumstances of what I see every day. My

00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:48.069
'want to'is great and I'm not

00:10:48.079 --> 00:10:50.629
giving up; I'm still standing on the Word

00:10:50.639 --> 00:10:53.310
because I know that He is going to bring

00:10:53.320 --> 00:10:56.150
forth the miracle. Abraham staggered not

00:10:56.160 --> 00:10:58.350
at the promise of God through unbelief

00:10:58.360 --> 00:11:00.550
but was strong in faith, giving

00:11:00.560 --> 00:11:04.110
glory to God, being fully persuaded that

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:07.269
what God had promised, He was able also

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:09.670
to perform it. Even with the deadness of

00:11:09.680 --> 00:11:12.269
Sarah's womb, even with the deadness of

00:11:12.279 --> 00:11:15.590
his wife's womb, he

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:17.949
staggered not at the promise of God

00:11:17.959 --> 00:11:20.910
because God promised him a son, Isaac. He

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:24.750
staggered not; his yielded

00:11:24.760 --> 00:11:27.150
'want to'was saying, 'God, I'm yielded to

